    {
      "id": "36",
      "name": "更多訊息",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "對話",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "日常對話",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 2,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "「要等待別人露出破綻...」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "貝蓮：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "怎麼了，要來打一局嗎？或許，我能夠從妳/你在牌局裡犯下的過錯中學到什麼呢...",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "對話1：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "那就來一局吧！",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "貝蓮（玩家勝利）：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "看來這次我不得不從自己的失誤中好好學習一番了。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "貝蓮（玩家失敗）：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "唉，總有人在自討苦吃...",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "對話2：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "不，暫時要做別的事...",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "貝蓮：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "嗯...那就等下次有空的時候吧...",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "七聖召喚",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "決鬥對局",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 2,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "關卡介紹",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "擁有高超牌技的「七聖召喚」牌手，雖然打牌時看起來有點心不在焉，但不會放過對手的任何一個失誤。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(204, 191, 173)"
                      ],
                      "text": "【提示】這是一位強大的牌手，建議牌手等級高一些再來挑戰。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "對手陣容",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3194,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/181140897/556aa3ebc88014c4c687823426d0b31a_9087663297877001943.png",
                      "menu_id": 17,
                      "name": "純水精靈·洛蒂婭",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
